            <title><![CDATA[中国成功发射遥感三十六号卫星]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/xinhuashe.jpg?itok=x2DQoVCQ" title="中国星期六在西昌卫星发射中心成功将遥感三十六号卫星发射升空。（新华社）" alt="中国星期六在西昌卫星发射中心成功将遥感三十六号卫星发射升空。（新华社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-10/xinhuashe.jpg?itok=x2DQoVCQ" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
